name: Hainan Airlines 787-8 "Dreamliner" Being Pulled to the Flight Line at Paine Field ᴴᴰ
description:
Happy Heavy Aircraft Friday!
For today's video, we have one of Hainan Airlines' Boeing 787 Dreamliner being pulled to the flight line at Paine Field. Not much was happening that evening at Paine, so I was pleasantly surprised when I saw this bird moving. What a gorgeous livery! I hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
